title: 'Pretty Little Liars' Star Janel Parrish Shares A Cheeky Bikini Snap
text:
'Pretty Little Liars' Star Janel Parrish Shares A Cheeky Bikini Snap Finding a secluded beach free of paparazzi is tough. Carly Ledbetter Associate Entertainment Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/14/2015 05:26 PM EDT 
Janel Parrish , also known as Mona Vanderwaal on "Pretty Little Liars," was recently snapped having fun in the sun with her musician boyfriend, Justin Altamura. Parrish and her beau ran into the paparazzi at some point in the day, when a photographer caught them at a funny moment. 
The actress poked fun at the incident by Instagramming a picture of it, captioning the shot, "Well ... the moment the paparazzi catch your boyfriend saying 'Ooh, I like that bikini.' #somuchforasecludedbeach." A photo posted by Janel Parrish (@janelparrish) on Oct 14, 2015 at 11:17am PDT 
A few hours earlier, Parrish Instagrammed pictures of the two on the beach, sans hidden photogs. A photo posted by Janel Parrish (@janelparrish) on Oct 14, 2015 at 12:43am PDT A photo posted by Janel Parrish (@janelparrish) on Oct 13, 2015 at 8:42pm PDT
